'''Clark Reid Martell''' (born December 23, 1960) is an American white supremacist, the former leader of Chicago Area SkinHeads (CASH), which was founded by six skinheads under his leadership in year 1987<ref>{{cite book|last=Atkins|first=Steven|title=Encyclopedia of Right-Wing Extremism In Modern American History|pages=115|publisher=ABC-CLIO|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=X7ad8GzRf0QC&printsec=frontcover#v=onepage&q=%22Clark%20Martell%22&f=false}}</ref><ref>{{cite book|last1=Forbes|first1= Robert|last2=Stampton|first2=Eddie |title=The White Nationalist Skinhead Movement: UK & USA,1979-1993|publisher=Feral House|pages=558}}</ref> the first organized [[Neo-Nazism|neo-Nazi]] [[white power skinhead]] group in the [[United States]]. The group was also called Romantic Violence, and was the first US distributor of [[Skrewdriver]] records and tapes.
