'''Lesbian, gay, bisexual, and transgender''' ([[LGBT]]) people in [[Alagoas]], Brazil enjoy many of the same legal protections available to non-LGBT people. Homosexuality is legal in the state.

==Recognition of same-sex unions==
{{main|Same-sex marriage in Alagoas}}
On January 6, 2012, the Court of Alagoas legalized [[same-sex marriage]] throughout the state of Alagoas, being the first to do it so. Now, same-sex couples don't need to have judge's approval to have a marriage license.<ref>[http://acapa.virgula.uol.com.br/politica/alagoas-regulamenta-o-casamento-civil-entre-gays-em-todos-os-cartorios-do-estado/2/14/15493 Alagoas regulamenta o casamento civil entre gays em todos os cartórios do estado - Brasil em Política no A Capa<!-- Bot generated title -->]</ref>

